    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330920/extras/f59a2f96a24f5a8155a2276872ddc850.poster.avif?t=1754372310\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330920/extras/f59a2f96a24f5a8155a2276872ddc850.webm?t=1754372310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330920/extras/f59a2f96a24f5a8155a2276872ddc850.mp4?t=1754372310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>&quot;这是一款治愈系的男男恋爱RPG&quot;</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >毕业在家无所事事的你被爸爸赶去隔壁小镇帮小时候邻居Jimmy筹备烟火节的摊位。而在这座小镇住着一些帅气的人们，他们都曾出现在别人的故事中。而这次，你将与他们谱写专属于他们的故事。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可攻略角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330920/extras/47524c07aafb7c1c877d59b0a433eb1f.avif?t=1754372310\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330920/extras_big/47524c07aafb7c1c877d59b0a433eb1f.avif?t=1754372310 width=800 height=385 /></span><i>&quot;每个角色都有自己的难题，但是都是温馨的故事，不会让你玩游戏还要忍受负能量喔。&quot;</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>悠闲的生活与积极的恋爱</strong>  <br>这是个半开放式的线性的小品，你将在这里度过几天的时间，在这几天你可以什么都不做，悠闲的体验生活，也可以谱写与这些NPC的恋爱故事。 </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时间系统</strong>  <br>游戏有清晨，上午，下午，傍晚，夜晚，以及深夜六个时段，地图中的移动不会推进时间，要透过事件来推进剧情。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330920/extras/0bdccd768e8285c55b44fb403ad8ed58.avif?t=1754372310\" width=800 height=200 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索街区</strong>  <br>游戏是横向转轴地图，在这有限的探索街区中有5位对象可以发展恋爱关系，你能成功掳获心仪对象的芳心吗?</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>内建事件树状图</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中可以查看所有重大分歧事件的树状图，你可以透过这个树状图来得知你错过了某个重大事件，但是如何到达那个事件，就必须靠你自己了。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330920/extras/35981c9d2e12db3e59ed8e8225448ee2.avif?t=1754372310\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330920/extras_big/35981c9d2e12db3e59ed8e8225448ee2.avif?t=1754372310 width=800 height=374 /></span></p>",
